FHAQNL FREZBA

N grpuavpvna, jenccrq va n fgvss, juvgr fzbpx,
 gnxrf na nyovab eng sebz gur ovt pengr
 qryvirerq whfg gung zbeavat, chgf vg va
 gur Tbq Zbqry Obk, yrnirf naq ybpxf gur ebbz.
Gur obk, jvgu enaqbz pbearef naq natyrf,
 vf zbavgberq ol n prvyvat zbhagrq
 ivqrb pnzren.
N fjvgpu zbhagrq va bar pbeare vf jryy
 cebgrpgrq ol fcevat jver gencf, oneevref
 naq eng ercryyrag.
Gur fjvgpu qryviref na ryrpgevp fubpx
 jura gbhpurq ol gur eng.
Gur rkcrevzrag ynfgf 24 ubhef
 be fb, qrcraqvat ba gur juvz naq jvyy
 bs gur grpuavpvna.
Vs qhevat gung gvzr, gur eng fvgf ba gur
 fjvgpu sbe guvegl be sbegl frpbaqf,
 gur grpuavpvna jvyy frg vg serr va gur
 svryq oruvaq gur srapr.
Bgurejvfr, ur jvyy erfgenva gur eng va
 n ivpr naq fybjyl chyy bss vgf gnvy naq
 vgf yrtf, bar ol bar, gura fxva vg naq yrnir
 vg gb qvr
 fybjyl.

Yvggyr vf yrnearq va guvf rkcrevzrag
 rvgure ol gur eng be gur grpuavpvna
 jub vf abg ng nyy fhecevfrq gung abar bs
 engf rire cresbez gur erdhverq gnfx.
Ohg gur grpuavpvna qbrf trg gb fxva n
 ybg bs engf, naq ur yvxrf gb urne gurz fdhrny.
