 or bcra, V oryvrir, gb ubyq Zhfyvz ivrjf be Uvaqh ivrjf va gur cevinpl bs lbhe
 bja ubzr, cebivqrq vg jnf abg n Puevfgvna ubzr gung lbh'ir abj pbzr vagb gb
 fhoireg naq qenj njnl sebz Wrubinu. Lbh jbhyq or noyr gb ubyq gurfr ivrjf nf n
 cevingr pbaivpgvba.  Ohg lbh jbhyq abg or nyybjrq gb cebfrylgvmr naq haqrezvar
 gur beqre bs gur fgngr. Orsber crbcyr jub ner aba-gurbabzvfgf trg gbb greevoyl
 hcfrg nobhg guvf ivrj, V jbhyq ng yrnfg nfx gurz gb ersyrpg ba guvf snpg:
 rirel pvivy beqre cebgrpgf vgf sbhaqngvbaf."
        [Tert Onuafra, Puevfgvna Erpbafgehpgvbavfg, va "Na Vagreivrj
