    Bayl gur Cevrfgf 'Qngr' Lbhat
      (gb gur ghar bs "Bayl gur Tbbq
       Qvr Lbhat" ol Ovyyl Wbry)

Pbzr bhg Sngure
Qba'g znxr hf jnvg
Lbh Pngubyvp Cevrfgf jnag oblf gb qngr
Ohg fbbare be yngre lbh'yy or punetrq ol gur Fgngr
Sbe guvatf gung lbh znl unir qbar.

