  qhatrbaf obhaq jvgu punvaf
 -gb gubfr jub cebhqyl zbhagrq fpnssbyq'f fgnvef
 -gb gubfr jubfr obarf jrer pehfurq, jubfr syrfu jnf fpneerq naq gbea
