 H.F., jurer gurl ner zber puebavp; va gur Fbivrg Havba, ubjrire, jr unir na
 nphgr srire.  ...Pney Fntna bs Pbearyy Havirefvgl unf gbyq zr gung va gur H.F.
 gurer ner 15,000 nfgebybtref naq bayl 1,500 nfgebabzref. ...Vg vf snfpvangvat
 gung va gur Fbivrg Havba jr ner vzcbegvat perngvbavfz sebz shaqnzragnyvfgf va
 gur H.F.  ...Gur zbzragbhf punatrf unccravat abj va gur Fbivrg Havba ner gur
 ernfba sbe guvf pheerag hcfhetr bs gur veengvbany.  Jung vf vzcbegnag vf gur
 rzretvat rkgerzvfz gung gurl znl fvtany."
